        "start": 3,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_065_000118",
    "sentence": "從莊宗定魏博，改突騎指揮使。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_065_000119",
    "sentence": "明宗即位，自隨駕左右廂馬軍都指揮授忻州刺史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "軍都指揮授忻州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 19
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 19,
        "end": 21
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_065_000120",
    "sentence": "歲餘召還，復典禁兵，領韶州刺史，出為大同軍節度使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "領韶州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 13
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
